<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV45">
<l>peruṅkēḻa lārtam peruṅkaṇ malarppuṇṭa rīkanammē</l>
<l>loruṅkē piṟaḻavait tārivva kāla moruvarnampōl</l>
<l>varuṅkēḻ pavaruḷa rētollai vāḻiyañ cūḻpiṟappu</l>
<l>maruṅkē varappeṟu mēcollu vāḻi maṭaneñcamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The great boar-man put his big eyes, blooming lotuses, on us,</l>
<l>altogether twinkling. In this untimely time, will there be any like us,</l>
<l>blessed ones, who come? “To us who are living of old, will any prospective</l>
<l>birth achieve to come to [our] side?” speak, oh ignorant heart.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
